License: CC-BY-ND-4.0 · TRIPOD-IP-v1.1

Catalogued: 142 public repositories across 13 categories.
Arbiter: nom (arbiter.py) — verifies every catalogued link resolves; verdict in data/arbiter.json.
Source: GitHub API (DavidWise01), generated by _gen_atlas.py.
Excluded: private repos, forks, and honey-badger (network-interception capability).
Self-contained index.html — registry inlined, rendered client-side, no dependencies.
